WEBVTT

00:00.805 --> 00:03.500
Previously on AMC's "Hell On Wheels".

00:03.676 --> 00:04.933
Tell me about Meridian.

00:05.000 --> 00:06.291
How do you know about Meridian?

00:07.224 --> 00:08.499
Are you a gunslinger then?

00:08.556 --> 00:11.056
I was just heading out west,
looking for work on the railroad.

00:11.294 --> 00:14.127
The thing's government
pays me per mile.

00:14.175 --> 00:15.388
You putting up a church here?

00:16.411 --> 00:17.511
You have to say the word.

00:19.301 --> 00:20.990
Nothing about... Maps being found?

00:22.000 --> 00:28.074
Advertise your product or brand here
